From: Acorn Build <build@acorn>
Date: Thu, 23 Apr 2026 18:42:22 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: invite-only auth, admin panel, accept-invite page,
 superuser role

- Superuser hardcoded to marketing@smartsure2020.co.za (always admin, undeletable)
- Admin Panel: invite users by email, assign role, view/update/remove team members
- Accept Invite page: users set password from invite link, then auto-redirect
- SignInPage: removed domain restriction, added invite-only messaging
- AuthContext: role now stored in Supabase user_metadata, set at invite time
- AuthGate: accept-invite path bypasses auth check
